h3. Message Dispatcher

Camel supports the [Message Dispatcher|http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/MessageDispatcher.html] from the [EIP patterns|Enterprise Integration Patterns] using various approaches.

!http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/img/MessageDispatcher.gif!

You can use a component like [JMS] with selectors to implement a [Selective Consumer] as the Message Dispatcher implementation. Or you can use an [Endpoint] as the Message Dispatcher itself and then use a [Content Based Router] as the Message Dispatcher.

